<subSubSection lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="5" pageId="5" pageNumber="4" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="5.[192,1440,1768,1929]" lastBlockId="6.[192,1440,217,581]" lastPageId="6" lastPageNumber="5" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[192,345,1768,1792]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">Comments.</emphasis>
The new species herein described is included in the fruticolus group, as it presents a beigegrayish green stripe on the pronotal disc, usually dark purplish lateral lobes of the pronotum, red hind tibiae and inferior valves of aedeagus long, twisted or tubuliform (
<bibRefCitation author="Descamps, M." box="[990,1184,1837,1861]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4" pagination="161 - 195" refId="ref14073" refString="Descamps, M. 1980. La faune dendrophile neotropicale V [b]. Seconde revue des Proctolabinae amazoniens et guyanais (Orthopteres, Acrididae). Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France. Nouvelle serie 16 (2): 161 - 195." type="journal article" year="1980">Descamps 1980</bibRefCitation>
). This group now has 14 species (including the new species), all of them, except this new species, are of Amazonian distribution (
<figureCitation box="[256,324,1904,1929]" captionStart="Figure 1" captionStartId="5.[192,275,1215,1237]" captionTargetBox="[531,1101,213,1182]" captionTargetId="figure@5.[533,1100,214,1180]" captionTargetPageId="5" captionText="Figure 1. Map showing the distribution of the Poecilocloeus fruticolus species group in South America." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3699431" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3699431/files/figure.png" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
): Peruvian species: 
<taxonomicName authority="Descamps, 1980" authorityName="Descamps" authorityYear="1980" box="[570,865,1904,1929]" class="Insecta" family="Baissogryllidae" genus="Poecilocloeus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bora">
<emphasis box="[570,658,1904,1928]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="4">P. bora</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Descamps, M." box="[665,865,1905,1929]" pageId="5" pageNumber="4" pagination="161 - 195" refId="ref14073" refString="Descamps, M. 1980. La faune dendrophile neotropicale V [b]. Seconde revue des Proctolabinae amazoniens et guyanais (Orthopteres, Acrididae). Annales de la Societe Entomologique de France. Nouvelle serie 16 (2): 161 - 195." type="journal article" year="1980">Descamps, 1980</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
