</taxonomicName>
(Napo, Aguarico river (San Pablo)). Colombian species: 
<taxonomicName authority="Descamps, 1976" authorityName="Descamps" authorityYear="1976" class="Insecta" family="Baissogryllidae" genus="Poecilocloeus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Orthoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="5" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="calcarifer">
